Insider Activity


Individual




Jeffrey H. Miro



Mr. Jeffrey H. Miro is Independent Director at L Brands, Inc., Senior Partner at Honigman Miller Schwartz & Cohn LLP, a Member at American Bar Association, and a Member at State Bar of Michigan. He is on the Board of Directors at L Brands, Inc.
Mr. Miro was previously employed as Independent Director by M and Chairman by Miro Weiner & Kramer. He also served on the board at Sotheby's Holdings, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Cornell University, a graduate degree from the University of Michigan, and a graduate degree from Harvard University.



