Jeffrey H. Miro: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 21, 2017 4:44 PM ET
Specialty Retail

Company Overview of L Brands, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Jeffrey H. Miro  Non-Independent Director, L Brands, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships74$268,837
Background

		Mr. Jeffrey H. Miro, also known as Jeff, has been a Senior Partner of Honigman Miller Schwartz and Cohn LLP since November 2004. Mr. Miro served as a Partner and Chairman of Miro, Weiner & Kramer from 1981 to November 2004. He has been a Non-Independent Director at L Brands, Inc. since July 31, 2006. He served as a Director of M/I Homes Inc., (formerly, M I Schottenstein Homes Inc.) since 1998. He served as a Director of Sotheby's (also called as Sotheby's Holdings Inc.) ... from April 1998 to May 8, 2006. He is an Adjunct Professor of law at the University of Michigan Law School, where he teaches taxation and corporate governance. He holds an A.B. Degree from Cornell University, a J.D. from the University of Michigan and an LL.M. from the Harvard University.Read Full Background




